sub_title: IBA Student at Rotterdam School of Management | Chairwoman of RSM Student Representation
summary:
I’m Kalina McCarthy, an International Business Administration student at the Rotterdam School of Management!

Born in Northern Ireland to a British father and Polish mother and growing up in Germany, I have seen the power that comes from different types of cultures and mindsets blending together. This has shaped me to aspire becoming a force for intercultural connection in the world.

Whether it is leading a student association, case solving, or simply studying in the modern and international city of Rotterdam, I continue to seek opportunities to challenge myself, always re-evaluating my perception of what a globalised world should truly look like.
